      "date": "2013-02-12 05:52:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ed84cc9c-74d5-11e2-93d9-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
